# Release Include Rules for Markdown Support Plugin
# Only files and patterns listed here will be included in release ZIPs
# Format: One pattern per line (supports glob patterns)
#
# This is the PREFERRED method (vs .releaseignore blacklist approach)
# Advantage: Explicit control, especially for selective vendor includes

# Core PHP Files
*.php
.htaccess

# Assets
css/
js/
i18n/

# Vendor (Runtime Dependencies Only - No Dev Dependencies!)
vendor/autoload.php
vendor/composer/
vendor/erusev/

# Documentation (User-facing)
README.md
LICENSE
CHANGELOG.md
